+## Overview
+
+Total revenue for the period is $7,154.44 across 30 orders. This represents a healthy volume of transaction activity with an average order value of $238.48 and a median of $204.94.
+
+## Top Products
+
+Gadget leads with $2,392.00 in revenue, representing 33.4% of total sales. Widget follows with $2,019.26, while Sprocket generated $1,540.00. Doohickey completed the lineup with $1,203.18, showing balanced product demand across the catalog.
+
+## Regional Performance
+
+North region performed strongest with $2,176.35 in revenue, followed by East at $1,830.79. South generated $1,732.48 and West contributed $1,414.82. North's 30.4% share reflects strong performance, while West underperformed regional averages.
+
+## Recommendations
+
+- Increase Gadget inventory allocation to capitalize on its leading revenue position and market demand.
+- Investigate West region underperformance and develop targeted marketing initiatives to boost sales penetration.
+- Promote Widget and Sprocket bundling opportunities to strengthen lower-performing SKU visibility and revenue contribution.
